name: F#@#! It´s Christmas Again
description:
"Very Funny Game" My Mom "Look, Yoda" My friend "Nice!" Ludum player

My elves,

 We are a week from Christmas, and I completely forgot about it. It’s your obligation to go to the old factory depot, and find some old presents. Be careful while walking there. Many traps and threats are waiting for you on those dark corridors. You have to get the presents before 23:59 of 12/24.
